2012年，意大利大薩索國家實驗室（Laboratori Nazionali del Gran Sasso）團隊驗證了铋-209α衰變的半衰期值，他們報告的數據是{{val|2.01|0.08|e=19}}年。他們還發現了铋-209經α衰變到铊-205的第二種路徑，即從铋-209衰變為铊-205第一激發態。這個反應的半衰期更長，估計爲1.66{{e|21}}年。<ref>{{Cite journal|author=J.W. Beeman|display-authors=et al|date=2012|title=First Measurement of the Partial Widths of <sup>209</sup>Bi Decay to the Ground and to the First Excited States|journal=Physical Review Letters |volume=108 |issue=6 |pages=062501|doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.108.062501|pmid=22401058|arxiv=1110.3138}}</ref>盡管這兩個半衰期都比碲-128的半衰期短，但其α粒子能譜的半峰寬是目前觀測到最小的，根據[[海森堡測不准原理|海森堡測不准原理]]估計分別爲ΔΕ~5.5×10<sup>-43</sup>eV和ΔΕ~1.3×10<sup>-44</sup>eV。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/hbase/quantum/parlif.html|title=Particle lifetimes from the uncertainty principle|access-date=2020-12-18|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013320/http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/hbase/quantum/parlif.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==用途==

[[钋-210|<sup>210</sup>Po]]可通過在核反應堆中用中子轟擊<sup>209</sup>Bi來制造。全世界每年<sup>210</sup>Po的產量約為100克左右。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.aljazeera.com/investigations/killing-arafat/swiss-study-polonium-found-arafats-bones-201311522578803512.html |title = Swiss study: Polonium found in Arafat's bones |publisher = Al Jazeera |accessdate = 2013-11-07 |archive-date = 2020-05-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200526214355/https://www.aljazeera.com/investigations/killing-arafat/swiss-study-polonium-found-arafats-bones-201311522578803512.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

==核合成==

在[[漸近巨星支|漸近巨星支]]的[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]中，铋-209和钋-210經由[[S-過程|S-過程]](慢速過程)通過中子俘獲而形成。此二核素是S-過程產生的最重元素。所有比它們更重的元素都是在[[R-過程|R-過程]]（快速過程）中形成的，該過程發生在[[超新星|超新星]]爆發前十五分钟。<ref>Chaisson, Eric, and Steve McMillan. Astronomy Today. 6th ed. San Francisco: Pearson Education, 2008.</ref>

